 {"id":"franken_networkx-wj9","title":"BUG: trophic_levels has dead code — unused dict comprehension on line 5802","description":"## Problem
trophic_levels() at __init__.py:5802 has dead code:
    {node: i for i, node in enumerate(nodelist)}
